``` java
    private final ConcurrentHashMap<E, Object> map;
```

改为：

``` java
    private final Map<E, Object> map;
```

或将其用Set代替

``` java
    private final Set<E> set;

    public ConcurrentHashSet(){
        set = Collections.newSetFromMap(new ConcurrentHashMap<E, Boolean>());
    }
```

